  ID: MalteseSoldier
  Name: Tommaso, Maltese courier
  Icon: {fileID: 409668665, guid: 4147f2bc6fccc974f937adc9cd1a5700, type: 3}
  Description: "He wanted a boat, not a weapon. His father told him carrying messages
    would keep him safe. A stone shard carved open his calf \u2014 the flesh is swelling
    black-green and smells like sweetness and rot.\n\nTreatment: Apply a high tourniquet
    until the foot numbs. Saw above the infection line in one clean movement. Cauterize
    or bind \u2014 either way, shock may end him.\n\nRequires: 1 Bandage"
